<center><h1> Situation Metaphor (Contd) </h1>

<h2><u> Interaction Model</u> </h2></center>
<h2>
<ul>
<li>  In the interaction model the mobile computer /device is a mediated
      tool between the user and his/her goal in the work space.</li>



<li>  The User Interaction is interpreted based on the physical location,
      time period,his/her activities and the contextual factors like
      companion, personal health,temperature etc. </li>




